{"type":null,"faqId":45448,"title":"华为盒子的无线显示（Miracast）如何使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">适用</span><span>：非华为手机，且手机支持无线显示功能（即手机支持 Miracast）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>进入华为盒子的“</span><span class=\"s1\">应用 &gt; 无线显示</span><span>”，启动盒子的无线显示功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165063\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>启动手机的无线显示功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>一般在手机</span><span class=\"s1\">“设置”</span><span>界面下，点击名为</span><span class=\"s1\">“多屏互动”、“无线显示”、“Screen Mirroring”或“ WLAN 直连</span><span>”的选项可启用手机的无线显示功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165064\" style=\"width:1.5430555in;height:2.2201388in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 4  </span><span>在手机上找到发现的华为盒子，并连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>等待几秒后，手机画面将同步显示在电视上。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果手机支持 Miracast，但有 HDCP 协议保护，可能也无法通过盒子将手机屏幕同步显示在电视机上。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>不同手机启用无线显示功能的操作可能不一样，若按照上诉操作无法正常连接，请向您手机的客服咨询该手机的无线显示功能如何使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":245,"faqType":"多屏互动","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"968","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Screen-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557782000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":77,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"无线显示,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}